<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_320px] gap-8 relative">
  <div class="bg-white/95 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 space-y-10 text-center">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">組み合わせたい言葉を選ぼう</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">あなたが選んだ 2 つのワードが、相手のひらめきの起点になります。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] gap-6 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">Word 1</label>
        <%= f.text_field :word1,
              placeholder: "言葉を選んでいません",
              class: "w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white text-center font-semibold shadow-sm focus:border-rose-400 focus:ring-rose-200" %>
      </div>

      <span class="text-3xl font-black text-rose-400 select-none text-center">✕</span>

      <div class="space-y-2">
        <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">Word 2</label>
        <%= f.text_field :word2,
              placeholder: "言葉を選んでいません",
              class: "w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white text-center font-semibold shadow-sm focus:border-rose-400 focus:ring-rose-200" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-2">
      <%= f.hidden_field :status, value: "in_progress" %>
      <%= f.submit "この言葉で作ってもらう",
            class: "w-full sm:w-64 mx-auto bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition" %>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-slate-400 text-center">Preview</p>
      <% [["ことわざ", @proverb.title.presence || "ないないことわざ"],
          ["意味", @proverb.meaning.presence || "意味"],
          ["用例", @proverb.example.presence || "用例"]].each do |label, value| %>
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl px-6 py-5 text-center text-base font-semibold text-slate-700 cursor-not-allowed select-none">
            <span><%= value %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/70 text-white text-sm font-medium opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">
            <%= label %>は相手が入力します
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <div class="relative group max-w-xs mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl px-6 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-slate-400 cursor-not-allowed select-none">
          投稿
        </div>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/70 text-white text-sm font-medium opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">
          投稿は相手が行います
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <aside class="bg-white/95 rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-6 space-y-4 self-start" data-controller="accordion">
    <div class="text-center space-y-2">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">一緒に作っているユーザー</p>
      <div class="border rounded-full px-5 py-1 inline-block bg-slate-50 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 shadow-sm">
        <%= @room.invitation.invitee.name %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button type="button"
            data-action="click->accordion#toggle"
            class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl py-2 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-slate-800 transition">
      使い方をみる
    </button>

    <div data-accordion-target="content"
         class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300"
         hidden>
      <p><strong>Step1.</strong><br>あなたが好きな言葉を 2 つ入力</p>
      <p><strong>Step2.</strong><br>「この言葉で作ってもらう」を押して相手に送信。</p>
      <p><strong>Step3.</strong><br>招待した相手がことわざ・意味・用例を仕上げてくれます。</p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
